#: ../../source/BeginnerSegmentation/BeginnerSegmentationPlugins.md:346
msgid ""
"You’re encouraged to explore the performance in some random images on your "
"own (you can do this from the `Test` menu with the `Random Image Set` "
"option), but if you find yourself consistently ending up with images that "
"look similar you can try examining images from the following list of wells- "
"A08, A12, B12, B18, C7, D6, D19, D22, E3. You can pick these with `Test` -> "
"`Choose Image Set`"
