#: ../../source/BeginnerSegmentation/CPbeginner_Segmentation.md:4
msgid "A computer exercise using CellProﬁler"
msgstr "تمرين حاسوبي باستخدام برنامج CellProfiler"

#: ../../source/BeginnerSegmentation/CPbeginner_Segmentation.md:7
msgid ""
"Beth Cimini, Barbara Diaz-Rohrer, Esteban Miglietta, Paula Llanos, Mario "
