"src=\"./TutorialImages/CellProfilerLogo.png\" width=\"40\">"

#: ../../source/BeginnerSegmentation/CPbeginner_Segmentation.md:61
msgid ""
"Figure 2: **Main CellProfiler window**. To load images, drag and drop images"
" into the right area. To load a pipeline (.ccpipe or .ccproj files), drag "
"and drop the pipeline file into the left area."
msgstr ""
